      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1234567890,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "输入：用户级样本 (单个用户的所有场景曝光)\nX^(0) = [H-tokens; R-tokens; T-tokens^S1; T-tokens^S2; ... T-tokens^Sn]\nN个多场景目标，来自N_S个不同业务场景",
      "fontSize": 13,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
